<i>noun</i>: 연주자 [연ː주자], 놀이꾼 [노리꾼], 광대 [광ː대] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>연주자 [연ː주자]</dt><br>
<dd>performer</dd><br>
<dd>악기를 다루어 음악을 들려주는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who plays a musical instrument to present a piece of music.</dd><br>
<dt>놀이꾼 [노리꾼]</dt><br>
<dd>1. performer; player</dd><br>
<dd>놀이에 참가하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who participates in a performance or play.</dd><br>
<dd>2. picnicker; sightseer; excursionist</dd><br>
<dd>축제나 유원지 등에 놀러 다니는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who goes on an excursion to a festival, recreational park, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>광대 [광ː대]</dt><br>
<dd>entertainer; performer</dd><br>
<dd>가면극, 인형극, 줄타기 등을 직업으로 하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person whose job it is to perform masques, puppet shows, tightrope walks, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>